76561198096565292,Recommended,310080,16645606,"Posted: 23 June, 2015",all,Mercury,"The creators of Hatoful Boyfriend made a huge gamble.Most of the people who buy this game just play it for the LOLs and to be able to brag about playing a dating simulator with birds (it's a great conversation starter, alright). They enjoy the derpiness for a bit, reach one ending and then move on to another game, some of them maybe a little bit disappointed.Well, it takes a few more completed routes to notice there's something really weird going on - you know, besides the whole bird-ruled society thing, andit takes ALL the character endings for the game to really start!Finally, all your questions will be answered! Why are the birds in charge? What happened to humans? Why was a human girl admitted to this super prestigious birds-only school? Why do the courses served in the school cafeteria have such morbid names? Why does the math teacher smell like bleach?If I hadn't decided to get all the achievements before being done with this game, I'd never have known how interesting it really is. As I said, a huge gamble on the creators' side, but in my case it paid off.Now, for those who are planning on playing this game, can you promise to actually complete it?>Yes>Yes>YesWhy thank you! I knew I could count on you!"
