,Recommended,310080,14059215,"Posted: 18 January, 2015",all,basedokosan | kickback.com,"To some, Hatoful Boyfriend is a game.To some, Hatoful Boyfriend is a fandom.To me, none of this amounts. It does not even come close.Let me tell you how my adventure went...A little background on me. I used to be a human soldier for the United States. I lost my legs in Afghanistan (Landmine+Humvee=Not Good). After coming back home to a wife who cheated and wanted a divorce, I fell into a deep depression. I thought my life was over and my existence had no purpose. That was, until I found this game.I thought this game was a joke. A bird dating sim?!? This'll be hilarious. It was even on sale! I invited some close friends over, we needed to kek together at this glorious joke.We booted up the game and set the graphics quality to ""fantastic"" Upon hitting play, our lives were changed forever.The screen lit up with the radiating energy of the sun, accompanied by the roar of 1 trillion lions. The angels of heaven rode down from Valhala one the backs of giant white doves, singing ""Hallelujah"" from their based lungs. Our eardrums deafened as the intertwining storylines of this gift from god put our minds on a new level. My computer exploded, but the game didn't stop. Because... we were the game.We were the game... and the game was us...Hatoful Boyfriend ascended us to a new state of being.A voice descended from the sky.""Coo!""(My children, it is time.)We were sucked into the world of Hatoful Boyfriend. The game is the way it is today because of us... we fixed the sins of this previously hellish world.It was time. We cured cancer, we ended world hunger, we stopped the birdocracy of the government.It was over... Everything was right in the world. so please, buy this game and let my hard work not go to wate... You won't regret it.10/10 Would travel interdimensionally again.pros:-weaving storylines-multiple endings-funny dialogue-clever writing-better graphics than crysis-better music tha