76561198080080021,Recommended,310080,28760995,"Posted: 28 December, 2016",all,AhstTraotee,"I bought this game on sale, and I almost regret not buying it at full price. This game is awesome.If you're curious about visual novels, but aren't really into the idea of playing a potentially NSFW dating sim (a.k.a. you're in the same boat as me), I recommend this highly to you. The concept of talking birds may be offputting to many, but I'm sure there have been cartoons and anime with stranger concepts. After a while, you'll likely stop caring that they're birds, and the script gently reminds you that you're a weird, freaky human through references to your hunter-gatherer instincts that you've honed through living in the wilderness.Each of the characters is a wonderful spoof of typical dating sim tropes (the senpai, the foreign exchange snob, the best friend, the nerd, the athlete, etc.), and the routes vary from sad to whimsical to just plain EPIC. And once you're finished with the routes... well, you've only hit the tip of the iceberg. This is a game that rewards the faithful, and your reward is a story you'll never forget as everything you thought you knew gets thrown out the window and reassembled in a whole new light.Trust me when I say you'll never look at pigeons the same way again."
