,Recommended,310080,12479642,"Posted: 13 October, 2014",all,Applefolf,"Hatoful boyfriend is a game one can never simply forget. True, it looks like a simple joke aimed towards visual novels and the like, however that is not the case. This game has enough to crush a player's heart through various ways but can also reward you with happiness on some routes. All the same, this game is more than meets the eye. The images and art used is high quality as standard, although a couple of birds do seem a bit blurry and pixelated. The English translation has been done well and I have only noticed a couple of minor errors (or what seem like errors) on the BBL ending. This should not deter you from getting this seemingly innocent game and playing it yourself, as the gameplay is superb and of a high quality overall.It was enough to make me cry a few times, and for my heart to swell quite a lot especially for one particular character (out of sadness).Final rating - 9/10This game is a lot less of a joke than the store page makes it out, so keep that in mind."
