,Recommended,310080,16705739,"Posted: 25 June, 2015",all,samuraiblue09,"This isn't just a dating sim with birds - it's much, much more. It challenges the social standings of humans and their place in the world - the world that humans have altered themselves for the greater good, only to have their creations turn against them. It touches upon the existance of the supernatural, and the consequences of mingling with fate and the higher order. The juxtaposition between the birds and the humans is highlighted as you interact with key characters. You will have to face with and debate against (or for) political issues that will directly affect your well-being. The more you, a human, gets involved into these affairs, the more you unravel about the hidden mystery behind St. PigeoNation Institute of Littledove Hachiman City.Would definitely recommend - you will not be disappointed."
