,Recommended,310080,29620612,Posted: 31 January,all,Captain Caesar,"This game is absolutely hilarious! Among all the other cutesy, gagging dating Sims and romance stuff, I'm glad to see a game poking fun at the genre in a well done, funny manner while still keeping the game enjoyable.I find the different endings great and I'm pleasantly surprised you can get some pretty evil endings. There's a lot of replay value if you want to get all the endings possible. I'd definitely recommend picking this up."
,Recommended,310080,29683198,Posted: 3 February,all,ʄǟռƈɦʏ ɮօɨ,"I had originally written this review on my page over a year ago. I had not beaten the game, yet I wrote a review on how it was cute and charming. After 100% completion, I MUST update it. While on the outside, Hatoful Boyfriend is just a game where you date birds, it is SO MUCH MORE! The core mechanics are those of a dating game, but every single storyline is so complete and emotion-jerking, it's insane. There are 15 endings to this game. The first 14 require you to complete the game by romancing each bird, some have true endings, where their story is given a proper conclusion, and you understand a little more about them. If you pick up this game, I do not highly recommend completing all of these 14 endings, I URGE YOU TO COMPLETE THEM. If you must look up a guide to beat them, then so be it, but they are all so incredibly amazing, and not one is a waste of time. Once you have completed these 14 endings, you will be able to complete the 15th, and final ending. Highlight over this area if you would like a semi-spoilery explanation, I won't say the story, and what happens, but I will say why you should complete all the stories in this game, here goes :Once you have completed the stories for all the characters, you are able to progress and complete the final story. This story will take the longest amount of time, as it is separated into 10 or so chapters. You will uncover every birds proper backstory through playing all the stories, you will be able to feel like you have just watched the most intense movie of your life. You will be plagued with mystery and anxiety, wonder and curiousity, and most of all, awe. It is absolutely incredible how JPEG images of birds with text boxes can make you feel such intense emotion. So once you're done with the first 14 stories of Hatoful Boyfriend, why not delve into the 15th story, and experience BBL. You won't regret it.This is one of the only games I have ever 100% completed, and with valid reason. This game was so compelling. Even if you're doing 1 story a night, or binge playing through the whole thing (average completion time maybe around 10 hours), you won't regret playing this game, and through it's stories. If you start it, I must request that you properly finish it. Please. You will not regret it."
