76561198049207950,Recommended,310080,16659386,"Posted: 23 June, 2015",all,Undying,"This game.  What more is there to say about this game beyond what has been said already?  It purports to be a bird dating sim, but under the zany surface, it is so much more.  There are multiple routes through the story, each matching you with a different avian.  Every route is some combination of hilarious, sad, and disturbing.  The writing is entertaining, and the game is very self-aware.  You'll think you're laughing at the game, and then you'll realize you've been laughing with it the entire game.But after you get your laughs (and maybe a few tears) from the dating routes, a new option will open up.  The ""Bad Boys Love"" route is the true heart of this game.  It is a well-written, fascinating, suspenseful tale that ditches the veneer of ""wacky bird dating sim"" completely.  All of the little details from each of the dating routes come together in unexpected ways.  I hesitate to say more, for fear of spoiling it, but rest assured, it's worth it.  You'll laugh, you'll cry, you'll encounter unexpected nightmare fuel, and you'll definitely never look at pigeons the same way again.So, really, to enjoy this game, you need to be a certain kind of person.  If you appreciate good writing, hold humor and serious (even disturbing) content in equally high esteem, and can get over the fact that all the characters are birds, give this game a go.  You might just fall in love."
