76561198119782159,Recommended,310080,16984120,"Posted: 10 July, 2015",all,Lessieal,"Interesting . . . .When I got this game I thought I could switch to see the human versions through out the play through.  I was wrong, and in away I am glad I was.  It's a simple game, many choices, I hear many outcomes.  I have decided to write this though now after only beating it once even if I plan to go back and play it many times again.I see people question why others like this.  My reason is, the characters even though they are basic you can feel and see a deeper meaning behind them.  Not being able to see them besides pictures of birds make you focus on their personalities even more.  It touches you more in that way, you're not just going for the one you like the looks of best.  In my eyes this is good for a game like this to have.  Allows you to open your eyes and realize what you may end up with just by feelings alone."
